                KU Center for Research on Learning
              </a>
            </div>
          </paper-material>
        </li>
        <li>
          <paper-material elevation="2">
            <div class="quote">
              <span class="quote-symbol quote-left">&#8220;</span>
              We like that Badge List is finding ways to unite ePortfolios and digital badging. 
