              <a href="http://www.competencyx.com" target="_blank" class="org-name">
                Competency X
              </a>
            </div>
          </paper-material>
        </li>
        <li>
          <paper-material elevation="2">
            <div class="quote">
              <span class="quote-symbol quote-left">&#8220;</span>
              The team at Badge List are wonderfully helpful. Their platform interface is 
