              classroom and professional learners.
              <span class="quote-symbol quote-right">&#8221;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
              <%= image_tag 'customers/logo-sccoe.png', class: 'logo' %>
              <div class="name">Cate Tolnai</div>
              <div class="title">Academic Technology Specialist</div>
              <a href="http://www.sccoe.org/" target="_blank" class="org-name">
                Santa Clara County Office of Education
              </a>
            </div>
          </paper-material>
        </li>
        <li>
          <paper-material elevation="2">
            <div class="quote">
              <span class="quote-symbol quote-left">&#8220;</span>
              Badge List makes it easy to celebrate students' and teachers' skill-based 
              accomplishments! Others can learn from experts already awarded the badge, building 
              a strong learning community.
              <span class="quote-symbol quote-right">&#8221;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
              <%= image_tag 'customers/logo-mar-vista-academy.png', class: 'logo' %>
              <div class="name">Mari Venturino</div>
              <div class="title">Blended Learning Specialist</div>
              <a href="http://mva.sweetwaterschools.org" target="_blank" class="org-name">
                Mar Vista Academy
              </a>
            </div>
          </paper-material>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="footer-text">
        To see more Badge List stories, 
        <a href="https://twitter.com/BadgeList" target="_blank">follow us on Twitter</a>.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- === ROW DIVIDER === -->
    <div class="row-divider top-orange-700 bottom-green">
      <div class="top">&nbsp;</div>
    </div>

    <!-- === PRICING ROW === -->
    <div class="row pricing-row">
      <h2>Badge List Pricing</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <div class="icon">
            <%= image_tag 'icons/globe.png' %>
          </div>
          <div class="body">
            <strong>Open Groups</strong> are completely free.
            Anyone can join and everything is public.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="icon">
            <%= image_tag 'icons/office-building.png' %>
          </div>
          <div class="body">
            <strong>Closed Groups</strong> offer advanced privacy and group management features. 
            Plans start at $5 per month.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="icon">
            <%= image_tag 'icons/school.png' %>
          </div>
          <div class="body">
            <strong>K12 educators</strong> receive special discounts. 
            Additional student privacy features are available.
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <a href="<%= pricing_path %>" class="button">
        <paper-button raised>View full pricing details</paper-button>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- === ROW DIVIDER === -->
    <div class="row-divider top-green bottom-grey">
      <div class="top">&nbsp;</div>
    </div>

    <!-- === FOOTER === -->
    <bl-web-footer></bl-web-footer>

  </div>

</bl-web-container>